        <description>I like building data process. A lot. And, unlike my stakeholders, I consider change, just the necessary step, that when implemented together, it makes a significant impact in their work life. Luckily for my stakeholders, I like resolving the business challenges even more.
I also quite like data visualization – charts and dashboards like sharable data interactions using the Shiny framework. Yes, I like looking at youtube videos of other people building data dashboards in my spare time.</description>
        
